the two opponents who will meet in the presidential election on the 26 th of this month are now in full preparation for holding the upper house .
the pro - western opposition leader viktor yushchenko is confident in winning the election . the pro - moscow prime minister , however , said that he will no longer represent the " ashamed " ruling party in the election .
meanwhile , russian president vladimir putin changed his attitude on ukraine 's accession to the european union , saying he was happy to see ukraine 's entry into the european union .
asked him , he was looking forward to winning more than 30 percent of the votes during the re - election , viktor yushchenko told reporters at the press conference : " conservative , i should get about 60 percent of the votes . "
on the other hand , from the appearance of his anxiety , adunkovic did not directly answer reporters ' questions . in the end , he only said : " we will win if we want to be the emperor . "
yvukovic , who was cultivated by the former president kuchema as his successor , has changed his course and defined himself as a candidate against the opposition party and the ruling party .
he said in a nearly direct name - name way : " i previously trusted cowards and traitors who worked under the government . now i feel disappointed . this government is really ashamed . "
kuchema exchanged conditions with the opposition parties by amending the law to transfer part of their presidential powers to the parliament to end the two - week - long large - scale opposition struggle and political chaos since the november 21 presidential election .
the original victory also came under the charge of the supreme court , which declared the election invalid and had to be re - elected because of widespread irregularities in the course of the election .
powell 's last visit to the hague to do everything for harmony between europe and the united states
us secretary of state colin powell held talks with senior eu officials today , during which he devoted his last effort to the unity between the united states and europe in his term of office .
powell 's trip to europe is aimed at repairing the diplomatic damage caused to both sides by the iraq war , and the hague is its last stop .
powell 's visit may be his last official overseas visit . the european union promised to him that the european union would advance toward the path of resolving tensions between the two sides before us president bush 's visit to europe in february next year .
however , differences between the two sides still exist .
foreign minister ablott of the netherlands , which holds the rotating eu presidency , said : " we must strengthen bilateral dialogue and find a common position during president bush 's second term . "
madam president of the european union 's foreign affairs commissioner , madam hua delaware , said she believed that europe and the united states have made progress in " putting the iraq crisis in the back of its head " . however , she also realized that " the present is a critical moment in european - us relations . "
bush will fly to brussels on february 22 to meet eu and nato leaders .
powell said that bush 's trip was aimed at repairing the cracks in the relations caused by the iraq factor .
powell has visited sofia and brussels during his trip to europe , but the progress of improving relations is limited .
in particular , in brussels , powell criticized the six nato countries that opposed the war for their refusal to participate in iraq 's training tasks , which has damaged the " reputation and unity " of their allies .
however , powell still insists that his meeting has shown the united states ' commitment to fully resuming diplomatic relations .
