us trade deficit reaches record high of 60 billion dollars in november
the united states ' exports shrank by 2.3 percent in november last year , bringing the trade deficit to a record 60.3 billion dollars , the commerce department said tuesday .
us exports dropped to a new low of us $ 95.6 - billion in five months . at the same time , because us import orders increased by over us $ 14.2 - billion in oil products to us $ 14.2 - billion , an increase of over us $ 2 - billion , and a growth rate of 1.3% , us imports grew by 1.3% , reaching a record high of us $ 155.8 - billion .
the trade balance rose 7.7 percent from the revised us $ 56 billion in october last year , and even a substantial increase of 50.8 percent from us $ 40 billion in november the previous year .
wall street economists predict that the trade deficit of goods and services will shrink to about 53.3 billion dollars , according to a survey conducted by the ibm market observation .
although the us dollar is weak and has made us - made products less cheap at home and abroad , the us trade deficit is still expanding .
the commerce department reported today that it would put pressure on the u.s. dollar and once again called on washington to do something about an energy independence in the united states and a trade imbalance between the united states and china .
the decline in us exports in november last year was due to a decrease of 1.4 - billion us dollars in capital finance exports , including a decrease of 325 - million us dollars in exports of aircraft and aircraft engines .
exports of industrial materials decreased by 800 million us dollars , mainly in the area of energy .
exports of motor vehicles , consumer goods and foodstuffs also declined .
japan respects neighboring countries ' dignity : defense minister
japan 's defense agency director general takahiro said today that japan would never forget the history of militarism and would remember the " dignity " of its asian neighbors when it took a relatively high international posture .
asked about the possible uneasiness that japan sent its self-defense force to the tsunami disaster areas in south asia , norota said : " when we come and go with southeast asian countries , we should never forget the past . "
he told reporters : " we must establish a kind of relationship with our friendly countries , so that we can tell our friendly countries that we have good intentions .
when we look back on the past , we should fully respect the dignity of other countries . "
norota particularly mentioned that this year is the 60th anniversary of the end of world war ii . he said : " we hope to revive and cooperate for the new era . "
norota has just finished his visit to several south asian countries hit by tsunamis . he said that when indonesian leaders told him that japan 's self-defense force 's disaster relief mission is completed by the end of march at the latest , he felt the " dignity " of an independent country .
the united nations has expressed concern over the deadline for the indonesian government to add foreign troops to it .
foreign troops ' aid and survivors of the most remote tsunami were well received .
nearly 1,000 japanese self - defense forces were on their way to the tsunami - stricken country on december 26 , killing more than 163,000 people .
this is japan 's largest deployment since the end of world war ii .
japan 's post - war constitution , which is dominated by the united states , stipulates that the self - defense force shall not use force .
political intervention in the content of the nmd hatch program ? japanese media set off the debate
it is reported that because of pressure from people in the political circles , the broadcasting corporation of japan ( nkk ) , a public - run broadcasting company , a few years ago , has shrunk in content when it broadcast a program aimed at imposing comfort women on the japanese army during world war ii . japan 's liberal media for this reason and its conservative stance .
it is said that the majority of the contents of the interview were deleted after discussions with senior politicians . most of the respondents were those who criticized japan 's wartime acts and those who were forced to be victims of comfort women . therefore , the liberal media criticized the practice of hatch .
the conservative newspapers , however , defended the decision to revise the content of the program , holding that senior executives of the company have the responsibility to ensure that the contents of the program are fair and objective .
the dispute broke out last week , and the key was a 2001 broadcast program aimed at mock trials of the japanese army 's offence of imposing comfort women during the war .
the trial was held by a women 's rights group in tokyo in december 2000 , and the court ruled that japanese emperor hirohito was guilty of permitting the japanese army to use comfort women during his occupation of various asian countries .
historians said that in wartime at least 200,000 young women were forced to serve as comfort women at the front - line japanese military 's warden . most of them came from south korea , but some were from taiwan , china , the philippines and indonesia .
well , the producer of the program , jing xiaowang , held a press conference with tears in his eyes on the 13 th , saying that before the program was shown , senior officials of the nkk had met with shinzo abe , member of the diet of the ruling liberal democratic party , and nakagawa , who expressed concerns about the contents of the program .
according to changjing , the upper echelons of the hatching program were subsequently edited and the contents were reduced .
he said , " i bow to political pressure . "
abe and nakagawa admitted that they had met with the staff of the nkk and told them they would be " fair , " but they firmly denied exerting pressure on the company .
euro zone data shows core inflation under control
economists said this week 's euro zone economic data would show that core inflation was still under control .
at the same time , both industrial production in the euro zone and consumer spending in france are expected to decline .
inflation is expected to rise slightly from 2.2% in november to 2.3% in december by the european union 's census and statistics department .
however , the rise largely reflected an increase in tobacco duty and the core inflation is expected to remain at 1.9 percent .
the core inflation figures will be released together with the consumer price data .
economists pointed out that core inflation , excluding food , energy , tobacco , and alcohol , has remained between 1.6% and 2% in the past two years .
the european central bank ( ecb ) said on tuesday that the price pressure has dropped recently .
while inflation is expected to remain at more than 2 percent in the next few months , it is likely to drop by the end of the year .
meanwhile , another economist said that industrial production in the euro zone on november 18 was also expected to decrease , due to a slowdown in german growth .
german industrial production fell 1.7% in november , while a survey conducted by the financial news agency on economists showed that euro - zone industrial production fell 0.4 percent in november after falling 0.5 percent in october .
us banks ' schmeding said industrial production in the euro zone is expected to rebound in december .
bureaucratic style causes two attacks on tsunami victims
three weeks after the worst tsunami attack in history , survivors are now fighting bad habits such as bureaucratic style and political command while global focus has shifted to other places .
thousands of decomposed bodies have been ferreted out one after another from the rubble , causing more than 168,000 people to die in the december 26 tsunami disaster . at the same time , the upcoming iraqi general election and president bush 's inaugural ceremony have replaced tsunami disasters and become the top news item on the media all over the world .
indonesia had asked foreign troops involved in humanitarian aid to withdraw within three months , but the request was recalled afterwards .
in thailand , leaders from canada , sweden , norway and finland are discussing the reconstruction plan and the identification of bodies .
however , survivors face new difficulties , such as the ingrained bureaucratic style in indonesia , which has hindered the distribution of relief supplies flowing into various parts of the world .
in a small village near the power station of the indonesian province of sumatra , the fisherman said , " we are in a house that does not exist at all . the tsunami has caused us to suffer heavy losses . we have lost everything and face hunger . "
he said , " we saw on television the food , clothing and other relief supplies flowing into aceh . "
like thousands of other disaster victims , brisbane has become a nightmare for him to lose his identity card and other official documents because of the tsunami .
although he earnestly requested the officials to go through the formalities every day , the result was the same : they could not get relief .
zeng qinghong reportedly went to visit zhao ziyang at the end of his life
chinese vice - president zeng qinghong went to hospital to visit former communist party of china ( cpc ) general secretary zhao ziyang , who died of illness , the information center for human rights and democracy said monday .
according to zhao ziyang 's family , zeng qinghong went to visit him at beijing hospital at 6 am . he passed away about an hour later at the age of 85 , the information center said .
zhao ziyang was dismissed from office as cpc general secretary and premier in 1989 because he opposed the use of force to suppress the tiananmen square democratic movement . he was then put under house arrest and has been regarded by the government as a non - welcoming figure .
according to zhao 's family , current premier wen jiabao , who had worked under zhao ziyang , did not visit him when he was in critical condition , the information center said .
however , before zhao ziyang fell into a coma on 14 august , tian jiyun , a retired member of the central committee who had served as his assistant , went to see him .
the information center of china 's human rights and democracy movement has kept in touch with zhao 's family , and for many years has issued the correct news on zhao ziyang 's situation at an appropriate time .
the center said that about 20 retired senior party , government , and military officials prepared to issue an open letter to the chinese communists , urging them to reassess zhao ziyang 's contributions , and asking them to hold public memorial meetings for him .
the center also said that zhao ziyang 's family would not be allowed to hold or make preparations for funeral arrangements and the party would have to make a final decision .
zhao ziyang 's wife , liang boqi , aged 86 .
because of her poor health , she said she had not been informed that her husband had passed away this evening .
china urged to promote democracy after zhao ziyang 's death
former chinese communist leader zhao ziyang passed away today , giving much respect to him , while japanese prime minister junichiro koizumi , the taiwan government and overseas chinese democracy movement all called on beijing to implement the democratic reform plan of zhao ziyang .
zhao ziyang was dismissed from office in 1989 for opposing military suppression of the tiananmen square democratic movement and spent his remaining life under house arrest . he passed away at the hospital in beijing this morning at 85 .
japanese prime minister koizumi said in memory of zhao ziyang , " i hope they ( china ) will strive for democratization . "
taiwan also called on china to carry out democratic and political reforms after zhao ziyang 's death .
overseas chinese democracy activists praised zhao ziyang as " one of china 's greatest reformists " and sacrificed his political life in order to oppose the bloody suppression of the tiananmen democracy movement .
lin shengde , former leader of the movement for free china in new york , said : " during his 15 years of house arrest , he openly advocated a political reform to march toward the rule of law and democracy .
zhao ziyang will be remembered by later generations as a real democratic and principled person . "
some pro - democracy activists urged the chinese government to hold a public funeral for zhao ziyang and to fairly evaluate his achievements .
however , they admitted that zhao ziyang was not likely to receive the protocol because the chinese government was worried that those who were dissatisfied with communist rule would take advantage of this opportunity to create turmoil .
the 1989 student movement was caused by the death of reformist leader hu yaobang .
xinhua news agency reported today that comrade zhao ziyang 's death from an illness in beijing was the only official statement on this matter .
rich countries fail to fulfill commitment to reducing poverty : un
a un - appointed panel of experts said in a new report that it promised to provide financial aid to the wealthy countries with a view to halving the world 's extremely poor population by 2015 , and at present it has not fulfilled its promise .
rich countries have promised to participate in the united nations ' ambitious " millennium development goals " program to improve the fate of poor and impoverished people in the world .
at present , however , there are over 1 billion people in the world living expenses for less than us $ 1 billion a day , and 2.7 billion people live on less than us $ 2 per day . un experts said that the time required for the rich countries to fulfill their commitments is almost left .
" through the correct mobilization of resources and political will , development and reform of developed countries , these goals can still be achieved , " said un development program director brown .
twenty - two rich countries have pledged to provide 0.7 percent of their gross domestic product ( gdp ) to developing countries , but they are now providing only 0.25 percent , un experts said .
un secretary general annan entrusted former harvard economist shks to write the progress report , which includes eliminating extreme poverty , popularizing primary education , reducing child mortality , and cracking down on aids and other fatal diseases .
the report said : " there is a practical solution . the political framework has been established . expenditure can be borne for the first time . now it is just short of action . "
united nations announces establishment of global disaster warning system
the united nations has announced the establishment of a global disaster warning system to prevent major natural disasters .
however , after the great tsunami tragedy in south asia , there is still controversy over the technology of that country in this disaster warning system .
un organizations said in a joint statement after a global conference in kobe , japan , that un experts will set up a global disaster warning system to reduce damage caused by natural disasters .
the major disaster caused by the tsunami disaster in south asia has angered all countries in the indian ocean .
" this new plan will bring peace and security to mankind , " said blix , head of the international organization for reducing disaster reduction .
an effective early warning system will ensure the lives and safety of millions of people around the world . "
but most of the un statement is symbolic .
unesco officials said that more consultations on this disaster warning system will be held .
unesco is taking the lead in promoting the establishment of a global disaster warning system .
aznar , director of the intergovernmental maritime affairs committee of unesco , said , " at present , several countries have put forward different plans , so we need to coordinate and cooperate . "
aznar said that the committee would hold two meetings within 60 days , hoping that the two meetings could decide on the adoption of that country 's tsunami warning system .
one of the meetings was held in paris and the other was not yet decided .
aznar hoped that a decision could be reached in july that the global disaster warning system would be completed by mid - 2006 , which is also the target date set by unesco .
aids infected people increase by 40 percent in beijing
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 1 ( reporters zhao xinpei and li xu ) the beijing municipal health bureau recently released the latest numbers of people infected with aids virus in beijing : from 1985 to october 2004 , beijing municipality reported a total of 2,046 hiv carriers , an average annual increase of 40.6 percent .
according to state statistics on aids , the number of people infected with aids in beijing municipality ranks eighth in the nation .
of the 2,046 hiv - infected people , 403 were from beijing , 1,507 from other places were from other parts of the country , 106 from foreign personnel , and 30 from their addresses .
according to analysis , beijing municipality mainly uses intravenous drug use and sex transmission , the floating population is mainly infected with aids by intravenous drug use and blood supply , and foreign people are mainly infected with aids .
to prevent the further spread of aids , disease prevention and control centers in 18 districts and counties of beijing municipality established free aids consultation rooms and antibody testing laboratories in july 2004 , carried out face - to - face consultations , initial blood screening and examinations , and epidemiological investigations , and will gradually extend them to hospitals at and above the city level .
the beijing municipal health bureau appointed the tiantan and you'an hospitals as hospitals for the free treatment of aids in beijing municipality , and the clinical part of the free treatment of aids . the required drug testing agents were purchased by the beijing municipal health bureau and the municipal financial and political bureau in a centralized manner .
the beijing municipal education commission has formulated a policy on free education for hiv - infected people and children and a policy on schooling for teenagers and students with hiv .
at present , hospitals in obstetrics and gynaecology departments at and above the second level in the whole city are responsible for free aids consultation , screening , and local tiantan hospital and you'an hospital for antiviral drugs treatment for pregnant women .
at present , the department has installed 1,390 automatic teller machines ( sets ) in its district free of charge , and a pilot scheme to maintain methadone treatment and to set up a clean needle exchange point among injection drug users .
shanghai records first world output in power equipment
xinhua news agency , shanghai , december 1 ( reporter jiang wei ) with the end of the trial operation of a 660,000 kilowatts generating unit , the shanghai auto - generators company , which belongs to the shanghai electric power station group , on the 1 st fulfilled its production target of producing 15 million kilowatts of annual production capacity and equipment , ranking first in the world in both output and production , realizing the long - cherished wish of several generations of people in china 's equipment manufacturing industry .
the shanghai electric power plant group is china 's largest power station equipment manufacturing base .
in recent years , due to the rapid growth of demand for power generating equipment in china , power generators across the country have entered a stage of high growth and great development .
after receiving four 1 - million - kilowatts class thermal power generating units , the shanghai electric power plant group has also obtained , through an overall tender , nine heavy gas - fired generating units and three remaining thermal - power boilers .
at the same time , through integrated operations , the efficiency of enterprise management , technological development , and production has been further enhanced .
at present , the shanghai electric power station group has already occupied 40 percent of the equipment market of china 's power stations , and has constantly expanded its overseas markets in such places as the middle east , southeast asia , and south america .
this year alone , as the main components of the power equipment , the shanghai auto parts company received an order for sale worth 6 billion yuan .
zheng jianhua , president of the shanghai electric power plant group , said : this summer 's " electricity shortage " has dramatically increased the demand for power station equipment in all parts of the country , and the competition for the manufacturing of power station equipment is getting hotter day by day .
this group is currently implementing the three major goals of " developing and manufacturing a - million kilowatts class thermal power and gas wheel - type generating unit and a - million kilowatts class nuclear power generation unit " in order to achieve the goal of becoming one of the top 500 in the world at an early date .
( hong kong , macau , taiwan ) hong kong observatory provides new services to wmo website
xinhua news agency , hong kong , december 2 , the hong kong observatory has been providing two new services for the world weather information service ( wwis ) and the severe weather information center ( swic ) , which are managed by the world meteorological organization ( wmo ) .
a spokesman for the hong kong observatory said that these two new services were the inclusion of official global weather observations on cloud amount and rainfall on the " world weather information service " website and the inclusion of tropical cyclone movement track in the " bad weather information center " website in the past seven days .
these two services are another new service provided by the hong kong observatory at the beginning of the year to provide the " severe weather information center " with official observations and data from around the world .
it is understood that the wwis has been providing official weather forecasts and monthly climatological information of major cities in the world .
for the first time , the new service provides official global weather observations and launches a global distribution map based on cloud amount and rainfall .
the new website weather observation covers a wide range of weather data with high density and is updated regularly eight times a day .
the new product on the website of the " severe weather information center " is a reentry function to provide tropical cyclone mobile route .
the previous design was that the website would no longer store information such as the location of the tropical cyclone before it dispersed .
however , there is still a general public wish to obtain relevant information on the tropical cyclone in the few days after the arrival of the tropical cyclone .
for this reason , the new product has stored the tropical cyclone grade , location and movement path in the past seven days , allowing the public and the media to obtain the necessary information within a few days after the tropical cyclone has landed and dispersed .
world 's first bird flu virus hatch 571 fast diagnostic agent successfully developed in shantou
xinhua news agency , shantou , december 3 ( zhang wenlin , lin jun ) reporters learned from the joint influenza research center of shantou university medical school and hong kong university medical college that they have cooperated with xiamen university in the past six months to develop the world 's first bird flu virus hatch 571 rapid diagnostic agent .
the quick monitoring method adopted to test samples of suspected people can reach a conclusion as soon as possible on whether to be infected with the bird flu virus .
according to the director of the joint influenza research center of shantou university medical school and the university of hong kong , based on information available at present , bird flu , which is listed as a highly toxic , deadly virus , has a very high mortality rate than the salem virus .
in the past , it took more than one week to close at three to five days from " suspected " to " confirmed " .
the avian flu virus quick detection technology that has been successfully introduced this time can , by adopting the method of enzyme immunity and gold standard , test the complete virus or fecal virus that includes excreta , mouth and mouth secretions , as well as blood clearing , and arrive at the earliest one hour or two hours at the latest .
with the simple , convenient , and fast features of new technology , more than 90 percent of new technology can be tested locally in the epidemic areas , and its accuracy rate can help to discover , diagnose , isolate , and treat the virus early , prevent the spread of large areas , and cause serious disasters .
entrusted by the china disease prevention and control center , the shantou university medical school of medicine and the joint university of hong kong medical college of medicine of hong kong recently held a training course on bird flu virus detection technology . the course included the latest avian flu virus rapid detection technology for students from 20 provinces and municipalities across the country .
fm commissioner 's office expresses strong dissatisfaction over speech by chairman of the international relations committee of the us house of representatives
xinhua news agency , hong kong , december 3 , a spokesman for the office of the commissioner of the ministry of foreign affairs in hong kong issued a statement on the 3 rd , expressing strong dissatisfaction with a recent speech made by haide , chairman of the international relations committee of the us house of representatives in hong kong .
the spokesman said : in his speech in hong kong on 2 may , mr. haide , chairman of the international relations committee of the us house of representatives , made malicious attacks on china 's development and progress and slandered china 's foreign policy with a cold war mentality . we express our strong dissatisfaction .
the spokesman said : as is known to all , china 's development not only conforms to the fundamental interests of the 1.3 billion chinese people , but is also conducive to the prosperity and development of the world .
china is a responsible country on the international political stage and has played a positive and constructive role in safeguarding world peace and stability .
on the issue of nuclear nonproliferation , china has always strictly abided by relevant international conventions , resolutely opposed nuclear proliferation in any form , and advocated resolving such issues through consultation , dialogue , and strengthening international supervision .
the spokesman pointed out : it is regrettable that mr. haider has ignored the objective facts . when sino - us relations are further developing in a healthy and stable manner , his extremely irresponsible remarks are completely inconsistent with the consensus reached by the chinese and us heads of state not long ago on the development of bilateral relations , and are relaxed in the mainstream voice of us society demanding the strengthening of cooperation with china . this is undoubtedly harmful to the development of sino - us relations .
china 's largest sea water desalination project starts
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , december 6 ( pan yifeng and xu qun ) up to now , the sea water desalination project , which has the largest scale and a daily handling capacity of 10,000 tons in mainland china , will settle down in the putuo district of zhoushan , zhejiang province .
for zhoushan residents , who are suffering from serious water shortages , hundreds and thousands of years of sea water rolling around them will soon turn into clear and sweet water , and water will flow into every household .
the hangzhou water treatment and development center of the state oceanic administration ( soa ) and the governments of six horizontal township in the putuo district of zhoushan city signed an agreement on cooperation in water desalination .
the first phase of the project , with an investment of 50 million yuan and a daily output of 10,000 tons of fresh water , will be completed next year .
zhoushan city is one of the cities in china with relatively serious water shortage .
there are a total of 1,390 large and small islands in the whole city , with per capita fresh water possession of 601 cubic meters . this is only 25.4 percent of zhejiang 's per capita possession . the issue of drinking water has always been a problem affecting the livelihood of residents of this island city .
take the lianyan town in the putuo district as an example , the daily delivery of 1,500 tons of fresh water from a nearby town , and the cost per ton exceeded 10 yuan .
the technology for anti-infiltration sea water desalination developed by the hangzhou water treatment and development center of the state oceanic administration is a process of separating the use of pressure as a driving force . it is a hot issue in the research field of seawater desalination .
a relevant person in charge of the center said : through technological improvements and equipment transformation domestically , the cost of anti - infiltration sea water desalination and the energy consumption have been reduced .
the cost of desalination and treatment for sea water per ton has further decreased on the basis of 5 yuan .
this indicates that the cost of seawater desalination is likely to be close to the price of tap water and industrial water .
( international ) hungarian referendum fails
xinhua news agency , budapest , december 5 ( reporter liu weimin ) hungary held a national referendum on the privatization of national public health institutions and the dual nationality of hungarian people outside the country on the 5 th .
the result of the poll was invalid because the number of voters participating in the poll and the number of people supporting the two issues did not reach the proportion prescribed by law .
a total of 30.11 million people cast their ballots late tuesday , accounting for 37.48 percent of the total number of voters in the country , according to the hungarian national election office .
among them , 19.19 - million people and 10.33 - million people voted for and opposed the first question respectively , accounting for 23.87 percent and 12.85 percent of the nation 's electorate , and 1.1518 - million and 14.26 - million respectively voted for and opposed the second question , accounting for 18.88 percent and 17.75 percent of the nation 's electorate .
according to the hungarian law , only the number of voters participating in the voting exceeds 50 percent of the country 's total voters , or only 25 percent of the voters voted in favor of or against the aforesaid issues can the voting result be effective .
earlier , the hungarian government and ruling party had called on voters to vote against the two issues while the opposition parties had called for an affirmative vote .
it is reported that this is the lowest number of voters taking part in the national referendum and the election .
after the result of the poll was announced , hungarian prime minister gyorgy announced his acceptance of the failure of the national referendum .
he said the government will take the initiative to formulate its national policies and carry out medical and health reforms .
the chairman of the confederation of youth league ( cdu ) , the largest opposition party in hungary , said that even though the number of people voted for the bill was not fixed , this referendum was beneficial .
he called on the government and congress to take into account the results of the national referendum when formulating the relevant laws .
wen jiabao stressed at an economic conference held by the state council that efforts should be made to raise the level of scientific and democratic decision making
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 6 , the state council recently held separate forums in zhongnanhai for local responsible persons , economic experts and scholars , and enterprise personages to listen to their views and suggestions on the current economic situation and on doing a good job in next year 's economic work .
wen jiabao , member of the standing committee of the political bureau of the cpc central committee and premier of the state council , chaired the forum and made an important speech .
huang ju , member of the standing committee of the political bureau of the cpc central committee and vice premier of the state council , attended the forum .
from 18 to 19 october , the state council invited persons in charge of eight provinces , autonomous regions , and municipalities , nine economic experts and scholars , and eight persons in charge of state - owned enterprises and individual private enterprises to hold three forums .
participants fully expressed their views on the international and domestic economic trends , consolidating the results of macroeconomic regulation and control , further strengthening agriculture , deepening the reform of state - owned enterprises , developing non - public - owned economies , improving financial services , guarding against financial risks , expanding employment , improving the social security system , and maintaining basic price stability .
wen jiabao and other leading comrades of the state council listened attentively to their speeches and discussed them with them .
after listening to their speeches , wen jiabao said : the state council will absorb and adopt many good opinions and suggestions while studying economic work .
he stressed : to implement the spirit of the fourth plenary session of the 16 th cpc central committee , an important task is to further improve the decision - making mechanism and make decisions in a scientific and democratic way .
this is an important measure for improving the party 's ruling ability and the government 's administrative ability .
as for major policy decisions that have a bearing on the overall situation of economic and social development , the government should conduct in - depth investigation and study through various channels and forms , grasp the true situation , and extensively pool the wisdom of the people , so that the policy decisions are truly built on the basis of science and democracy .
wu yi , zeng peiyan , hui liangyu , hua jianmin , other leading comrades of the state council , and responsible persons of relevant departments separately attended the forum .
( international ) alegrett council meets in peru
xinhua news agency , kusiko , december 7 ( reporter : liu guoqiang , wang lulu ) the presidential council of the andes community opened its special meeting on the 7 th in the famous tourist city of peru .
the presidents or representatives attending the meeting will discuss such issues as deepening the andes - oriented regional integration plan and promoting economic and social development .
speaking at the opening ceremony , peruvian president alejandro toledo said that although the andean group has been established 35 years ago , it has not yet been solved on major issues such as poverty .
at present , the poverty rate in the andes region is as high as 53 percent , which constitutes a serious threat to the democratic administration in the region .
to this end , the governments of the andean countries should strive to explore and establish an effective mechanism to shake off poverty and increase people 's participation in state affairs in order to promote social stability and development .
toledo pointed out that although there are still many problems in the andean group , great progress has been made in the process of latin american integration in recent years , and the south american community will announce the establishment of the third south american summit here on wednesday .
he expressed the belief that the establishment of this new regional organization will play an important role in promoting regional political , economic , and social development .
besides toledo , bolivian president meta also attended the meeting .
colombian president gutierrez and venezuelan president chavez were unable to attend the summit due to various reasons . however , they will come here to attend the third south american summit on 8 april .
the andes community was founded in 1969 and is composed of five countries , namely bolivia , colombia , ecuador , venezuela , and peru . it is a regional organization for latin american countries to conduct economic cooperation . its headquarters is in lima , the capital of peru .
the president 's council is the highest decision - making body for the andean group , which meets once a year .
the last meeting was held in the capital city of ecuador in july 2003 .
construction of three gorges underground power station to start soon
xinhua news agency , wuhan , december 8 ( reporter shi yongfeng ) on december 8 , the main body of the yangtze river three gorges project underground power station held its first open tender , thus opening the curtain of the construction of the three gorges underground power station .
the three gorges project has designed and installed 26 generating units of 700,000 kilowatts , with an installed capacity of 18.2 million kw and an average annual electricity generation of 84.7 billion kwh .
in order to further tap the power generating potential of the three gorges project , the three gorges project has set aside , in its preliminary design , a position for expanding the underground power station .
according to a briefing given by the person in charge of the china three gorges project development corporation , the three gorges underground power station is deployed on the mountain body on the right bank of the three gorges dam . its main buildings include water tower , water diversion tunnel , main plant , tail water system , parent line pits , 500 kerosene power station , and so on .
six generating units of 700,000 kilowatts will be installed at the underground power station .
in this way , the installed capacity of the three gorges project will be increased from 26 to 32 , with the installed capacity increasing from 18.2 million kilowatts to 22.4 million kilowatts , thus greatly increasing the power generation capacity of the three gorges project .
flood prevention is the most important task of the three gorges project .
according to the plan for the operation of the three gorges reservoir , the water level in the reservoir will be lowered from 175 meters in normal water storage to 145 meters in flood prevention water before the flood season .
therefore , the construction of the underground power station will increase the use of water for the three gorges reservoir , reduce the use of water and increase electricity generation , and maximize the time required for the power station not to abandon water consumption .
at present , the construction of the three gorges underground power station 's preliminary projects , such as the excavation of the subhole , the excavation of the tail section , and the repair and maintenance of the sub - section , has begun .
it is understood that all the underground power stations will be completed and put into production by the end of 2008 .
china 's maritime festival is ready to come out
xinhua news agency , beijing , december 8 ( reporter huang fuhui ) at a news conference held here on the 8th , yao mingde , president of the china road transport association , expressed " full confidence " in the establishment of the china sea route festival .
