it has been learned that the state council should approve the establishment of a holiday that does not require leave .
zheng he is a famous maritime ship in the world .
during the 28 years from 1405 to 1433 , zheng he led more than 200 ships and nearly 30,000 people to travel across the sea seven times to southeast asia and the indian ocean . he traveled more than 300,000 kilometers and traveled to more than 30 countries and regions in asia and africa .
china will hold a series of activities next year to mark the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's voyage to the west .
signs of the commemorative activities were issued in beijing on the 8th .
the logo is made up of a sailing ship sailing west by braving the wind and waves , a billowing light blue arc flower , and a written word " the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's maritime expeditions " .
the designer is yao ying , art teacher of no . 1 xian high school in shaanxi province .
people of all walks of life in society have appealed to seize the opportunity of the 600 th anniversary of zheng he 's maritime expeditions in 2005 and the strengthening of adult education to establish a navigation festival in china in order to raise people 's maritime awareness and maritime awareness , carry forward the spirit of the chinese nation , and deepen education in patriotism .
yao mingde said : china has more than 3 - million square kilometers of sea area . in china 's international trade , 90 percent of its goods are completed by sea .
as china is a big maritime power in the world , it is unnecessary for china to have no sea - going festivals in many festivals .
taiwan province has designated july 11 as its maritime day .
there are sea festivals in more than 10 countries in the world , such as the united states , canada , and japan .
