xinhua news agency , beijing , january 15 , state council premier wen jiabao signed the state council decree no. 430 on the other day to promulgate the " regulations on protecting the safety of railway transportation . "
the " regulations " are divided into 103 articles and will come into force as of 1 april 2005 .
the " regulations " were formulated in accordance with the " prc law on railway development " and the " prc law on safe production " in order to strengthen the safety management of railway transportation , ensure the safety and smooth flow of railway transportation , and protect personal safety , property safety , and other legitimate rights and interests .
the " regulations " point out that the state council 's railway administration is in charge of supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation nationwide .
the railway management institution set up by the state council 's railway administration is responsible for supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation in the region .
according to the " regulations , " local people 's governments at all levels and people 's governments at and above the county level in the areas along the railway should , in accordance with their respective responsibilities , do a good job in supervising and managing the safety of railway transportation , step up education in railway transportation , implement a responsibility system for protecting the safety of railway transportation , prevent and stop behaviors that endanger the safety of railway transportation , and coordinate and handle relevant safety matters in railway transportation .
the " regulations " point out : public security organs should share their responsibilities and responsibilities in order to maintain law and order in railway stations , trains , and other places and to maintain law and order along railway lines .
railway transportation enterprises should strengthen the management of railway transportation safety , establish and improve the production safety management system , set up safety management institutions , and ensure the investment of funds needed for the safety of railway transportation .
railway transportation personnel should stick to their posts , work according to procedures , fulfill their duties , and ensure transportation safety .
( international ) overseas chinese in japan support china 's formulation of anti - secession law
xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 18 ( reporter : yue shaoyan ) - the china council for promoting peaceful reunification held a meeting at the zhongshan memorial hall in yokohama a few days ago , expressing firm support for the chinese government 's anti - secession law and its efforts to promote the great cause of the reunification of the motherland .
the meeting held that " taiwan independence " is the greatest danger to the interests of the taiwan compatriots and is the greatest threat to the situation in the taiwan strait .
enactment of the anti-secession law is conducive to cracking down on taiwan independence forces and their separatist activities , and is conducive to peace and stability in the taiwan strait and the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation . fundamentally speaking , it is for protecting the vital interests of the taiwan compatriots and is a legal guarantee for realizing the aspirations of the broad masses of taiwan compatriots for peace , stability , and development .
the meeting also adopted a statement , expressing firm support for the government in formulating anti - secession law and safeguarding china 's reunification .
the statement says : the extremely separatist activities of the " taiwan independence " forces have fundamentally undermined the one - china principle and harmed the fundamental interests of the chinese nation .
it is the common will of overseas chinese and compatriots on both sides of the taiwan strait to check the separatist acts of " taiwan independence " elements through legislation .
the statement held : the formulation of the anti - secession law has fully demonstrated the great sincerity of the chinese government and people in upholding peaceful reunification and their firm determination to resolutely safeguard state sovereignty and territorial integrity . it has won the people 's support and the broad masses of overseas chinese and foreign nationals of chinese origin in japan completely support it .
the federation of overseas chinese and chinese nationals in japan , the overseas chinese association in tokyo , and the association of people of taiwan province also issued statements on the same day , expressing their support for china 's formulation of an anti - secession law and its determination to safeguard national unity .
( international ) lima , the capital of peru celebrated 470 th anniversary of founding
xinhua news agency , lima , january 18 ( reporter wang lulu ) on the 18th , citizens of peru 's capital lima held a grand , rich and colorful cultural and entertainment activity in all parts of the city to solemnly celebrate the 470 th anniversary of the city 's founding .
public venues such as the lima city park and church held various celebration activities organized by the municipal government and non-governmental organizations on the same day , including large - scale jemaah islamiyah , sales of ethnic products , and the famous peruvian " infantry horse " performance .
lima mayor louis kastase said the long - standing city is moving toward standardization and modernization , adding that he will put the improvement of the city 's economic environment and the improvement of its social services in the most important position of urban development .
on the evening of the 17 th , nearly 3,000 citizens watched a brilliant song and dance evening party held by the city government at the weapons square in the city center . the colorful light decorated the old buildings around the square . famous song and dance artists put on ethnic dances and dances of different regions .
the residents also watched beautiful fireworks and firecrackers and celebrated the night together .
on 18 january 1535 , spanish adventurer pella came to the bank of the marble river and erected government house , claiming that this was to express respect for then spanish king juan carlos v and queen anna , so lima was called the " city of king . "
lima has become the national political , economic and cultural center since peru gained independence in 1821 .
at present , lima 's urban area has grown from 2.14 square kilometers in the early days of its founding to more than 2,600 square kilometers and its population has increased to about 8 million , accounting for 31 percent of the country 's total population .
( international ) argentine vice president and senate president meet with li tieying
xinhua news agency , buenos aires , january 19 ( reporter cao yu and shen an ) argentine vice president and senate president xiao li met with the visiting chinese npc delegation headed by li tieying at the government palace on the 19 th . he said he hoped to further strengthen the friendly and cooperative relations between argentina and china in all fields .
xiao li said : in 2004 , the two countries achieved mutual visits by top leaders , established a strategic partnership , signed a series of agreements on friendly cooperation , and constantly developed friendly relations between the two countries .
at present , the relations between the two countries are in the best period in history , and i hope that in the future , the two sides will further strengthen their comprehensive cooperation , especially exchanges between the argentine national assembly and the chinese npc .
xiao li said : argentina attaches great importance to developing a strategic partnership with china and learning from china 's valuable experience in economic development .
argentina agrees with the one - china stand .
li tieying first conveyed chairman wu bangguo 's regards to vice president xiao li and senate president .
li tieying said : the exchange of visits between argentine president basque and chinese state president hu jintao in 2004 has decided to establish a strategic partnership , and sino - argentine relations have entered a new stage .
the chinese government attaches great importance to developing relations with all latin american countries , including argentina .
li tieying said : the chinese government appreciates argentina 's adherence to the one - china stand .
li tieying and his entourage arrived in buenos aires on 18 april for a friendly visit to argentina at the invitation of the argentine national assembly .
he also met with argentine chamber of deputies speaker manoumando .
the chinese npc delegation headed by li tieying will also pay friendly visits to uruguay and brazil .
( international ) cis collective security treaty plans to increase military strength to deal with threats
xinhua news agency , moscow , january 20 , bozza , secretary general of the organization of collective security of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) , said on the 20th that the organization would strengthen its military strength to deal with contemporary major threats such as international terrorism , drug trafficking , illegal immigration , and organized crime .
boroza said in his speech at an international seminar on the organization of the collective security treaty of the commonwealth of independent states ( cis ) held in moscow on the same day that the group currently being set up in central asia will have a series of practical measures to protect them , and during the process of their establishment they will draw on the experience of russian and belarus joint forces in eastern europe and russian and armenian troop clusters in the caucasus .
he said : according to the joint military construction plan up to 2010 , the organization will establish a unified air defense , communications , and information investigation and support system in the central asian region .
at the same time , unified standards for military training will also be drawn up and relevant material and technological reserves will be established .
bolshoi said that the establishment of the cis rapid reaction force is helpful in curbing extremist forces in central asia , and the force has demonstrated this strength during last year 's military exercises .
he stressed that the group would not use troops in regions other than the member states .
the cis collective security treaty organization includes russia , armenia , kazakhstan , kyrgyzstan , tajikistan , and belarus .
its predecessor was the cis collective security treaty signed by the six countries in 1992 .
in may 2002 , the cis collective security treaty council decided to change the " cis collective security treaty " to the " cis collective security treaty organization " and set up a military management organ for the collective security treaty .
beijing also issues seven safety management standards for " crowded places "
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 24 ( reporters zhang shanwang and wang wentao ) the beijing municipal bureau of commerce , the beijing municipal bureau of culture and the beijing municipal bureau of forestry issued on the 24th seven safety management standards for " crowded places " such as shopping malls and parks .
lu hao , vice mayor of beijing , believes that the formulation and release of these seven standards of safety management is a concrete embodiment of beijing 's standardization of safety quality .
among the seven pilot safety management regulations , namely , " safety management standards for beijing municipality 's commercial performance venues ( trial implementation ) , " " safety management standards for internet service business sites ( trial implementation ) , " " safety management standards for beijing municipality 's internet service sites ( trial implementation ) , " and " safety management standards for beijing 's parks , scenic spots , and places of historical interest ( trial implementation ) , " we have also strictly standardized figures .
liu chaogao , chief engineer of the beijing municipal landscape bureau , told this reporter that the park management organization has for the first time studied and made explicit stipulations on the area of operation and the number of visitors involved in each of the seven " regulations , " such as the " safety management standards for beijing municipality 's parks and scenic spots ( trial points ) . "
the seven " regulations " will be put on trial on a trial basis within two months before and after the spring festival and will be formally implemented on 24 march 2005 .
